{"tid":647091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[另類反擊？]中科院 甘肅項目請道士驅邪","createTime":"2018-04-29T14:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T14:41:36.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5abb1a817d4270ba115c366ec2c354d659656abe","tid":647091,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T14:36:15.000Z","msg":"內地一名作家張弓上周四（26日）透過微信公眾號發文，指中科院位於甘肅武威市的一個項目舉行奠基儀式時，竟然出現請道士做法事等迷信行為。文章迅即在網上廣泛傳播，當地縣政府上周五（27日）向傳媒澄清，指當日的活動是施工企業安排，強調官方知情後已即時制止。<br />\n<br />\n從現場短片可見，事發地盤的土地已被完全鏟平，並豎立了一道巨大的拱門及多條巨型充氣立柱，旁邊則有多輛大型施工機械。而拱門的正前方則設有一張祭台，上方擺放了水果及道士所用的法器。在法事開始後，一名男子焚燒黃表紙，現場有人吹嗩呐、擊鼓奏樂。而道士則身穿道袍、手執符咒，對着一隻被殺死放血的羊和祭台念咒語。<br />\n<br />\n有北京傳媒周四致電中科院李姓相關負責人了解，但對方聽到此事後立即掛斷電話，拒絕回應。而民勤縣委辦公室工作人員就回應指，是施工企業自行在奠基儀式上，請來道士做法事、驅邪保平安，與政府無關。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180429/bkncn-20180429010132207-0429_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180429%2Fbkncn-20180429010132207-0429_05011_001.html&d=sSYdjU7C7ik4kpV3FL79f4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=749b622c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180429/bkncn-20180429010132207-0429_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a073afc979ef0097fead256eb29c3050fd8f44ed","tid":647091,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T14:36:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180429/photo/bkncn-20180429010132207-0429_05011_001_04b.jpg?20180429010400\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180429%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180429010132207-0429_05011_001_04b.jpg%3F20180429010400&h=f8311a52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180429/photo/bkncn-20180429010132207-0429_05011_001_01b.jpg?20180429010400\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180429%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180429010132207-0429_05011_001_01b.jpg%3F20180429010400&h=1012e12a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15286a955d77199def19fd6c567f825a19175e33","tid":647091,"uid":106633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T14:37:29.000Z","msg":"贏國傳統科學"},{"pid":"b70568db0811398862dbd8f57a5e72bab485d7a4","tid":647091,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T14:37:57.000Z","msg":"風水抗美陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又贏"},{"pid":"f642ff394d6063afa130170e215058698fe21aa3","tid":647091,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T14:38:02.000Z","msg":"儀式同迷信係兩樣野黎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a39e5880b38510425da38c664bdcbaeb5e1ace","tid":647091,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T14:41:36.000Z","msg":"呢個只係儀式，禮儀來<br />\n好似上面巴打講<br />\n<br />\n等同請麥鈴鈴出席下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}